    dc:creator "Pauly, Alain; Devalez, Jelle; Sonet, Gontran; Nagy, Zoltán Tamás; Boevé, Jean-Luc" ;
    dc:date "2015" ;
    dc:title "DNA barcoding and male genital morphology reveal five new cryptic species in the West Palearctic bee Seladonia smaragdula (Vachal, 1895) (Hymenoptera: Apoidea: Halictidae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.244992>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.244983>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.244993>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.244984> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.244992>
    dc:description "FIGURE 23. Ventral view of the large projection of the male gonocoxite of Seladonia gemmella sp. nov., S. submediterranea sp. nov. and S. orientana sp. nov. Left photographs are reproduced from Pauly & Rassel (1982), at right new photographs by Pauly & Cillis; a, S. gemmella (Spain, Alicante); b, S. gemmella (Spain, Almeria); c, S. submediterranea (Romania, Bucarest); d, S. submediterranea (France, Deux-Sèvres); e, S. orientana (Croatia, Ugljan); f, S. orientana (Greece, Samothrace)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/244992/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.244983>
    dc:description "FIGURE 14. Seladonia submediterranea sp. nov., male holotype (= form C) (France, Deux-Sèvres, Saint-Martin-de- Bernegoue), ventral view of the projections of the gonocoxites." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/244983/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.244993>
    dc:description "FIGURE 24. Contour of the small projection, in lateral view, of the male gonocoxite in the species of the Seladonia smaragdula complex; a, S. smaragdula (Spain, Almeria); b, S. phryganica sp. nov. (Greece, Anafi); c, S. gemmella sp. nov. (Spain, Almeria); d, S. cretella sp. nov. (Greece, Crete); e, S. submediterranea sp. nov. (France, Deux-Sèvres); f, S. orientana sp. nov. (Greece, Lesvos)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/244993/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.244984>
    dc:description "FIGURE 15. Geographic distribution of Seladonia submediterranea sp. nov. (males with genitalia form C, barcoded females from Southern Europe and females from Central Europe)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/244984/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

